5000|$|<b>Recoupment.</b> Where {{one person}} {{discharges}} the debt of another, {{he or she}} may be able to sue the debtor and thereby recoup the loss. Historically, this was a quasi-contractual action known as an action for money paid, laid out and expended to the defendant's use.|$|E
